間asso 咩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKUSPACE HD</blockquote><br />\nBtw係咪nfm/food health?"},{"pid":"67611e320286e843ccc94773d2ada7f8255a5840","tid":186261,"uid":70300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實cu都好似有biomedical science讀<br />\n不過如果你唔太熟悉natural sciences嘅話可以講多少少俾你聽<br />\n<br />\n其實佢同4年制嘅science分別在於<br />\n1. 讀2年rather than 4年<br />\n2. 一入就要決定7個concentration入邊一個，之後就跟住各個conc嘅要求揀elective courses讀，當中要求一定要讀嘅required course係每個conc都唔同。而揀elective方面，biological science可以揀嘅course係最多，我地叫最有彈性。<br />\n3. 佢讀69cred畢業<br />\n<br />\n至於出cert方面聽講係出Bsc in Natural Sciences,唔知會唔會出埋邊一個conc,你有興趣知嘅話我可以幫你問下，咁啱今日有consultative meeting。<br />\n<br />\nUlife方面一定係cu唔使諗，有得無限dem beat，啲can又好食，地方環境又舒服，<br />\n<br />\n利申現屆natural sciences programme society嘅p 有咩唔明可以再問</blockquote><br />\n其實city biomedical sciences同cu natural science 都比左offer我。cu 個conc 就係biological science。所以我諗緊點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。cu natural science 嘅認受性會唔會低過4年制嘅cu science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09be77d3d5c7fd397df4c68e7152f97c602fbc06","tid":186261,"uid":70300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗左好耐都諗唔到 其實city biomedical sciences 讀嘅野 cu natural science 都有得讀，而且cu 又三大。不過city biomedical sciences 就聽聞可以考牌做MLT, cu 就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求各位巴絲指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n介唔介意講邊間asso 咩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKUSPACE HD</blockquote><br />\nBtw係咪nfm/food health?</blockquote><br />\nmedical"},{"pid":"0e733872407ae3ff75686fac2d585afde8e51a29","tid":186261,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:34:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔考個乞衣牌出黎行乞"},{"pid":"1f089cb2294663eee4326f9eef17ad749cb0cc1d","tid":186261,"uid":29708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n其實city biomedical sciences同cu natural science 都比左offer我。cu 個conc 就係biological science。所以我諗緊點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。cu natural science 嘅認受性會唔會低過4年制嘅cu science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好坦白講，讀嘅course同4年制嘅係一樣，會一齊上堂，學嘅野一樣又拉同一條curve，只係有少部份嘅course係reg唔到，不過有興趣讀都可以私底下同prof講或者同office講，好多時學校都會盡量幫，依樣野係幾好嘅。<br />\n<br />\n認受性個方面，依個program係ugc-funded，理應同其他program睇齊，再講出面大部份都係睇你邊間大學出嚟，若果搵工搵個啲需要有specific/relevant scientific background嘅話，你可以再作補充，你真係讀過識嘅點都係事實，show到出嚟就無問題。<br />\n<br />\n拎個例子嚟講，有某啲政府部門請理科人，佢會寫明係自然課學都得，只於識唔識做佢列出嚟嘅職責多數都係睇你有無讀過相關嘅course，有陣時無都可能收，不過要你再學下點做。"},{"pid":"d3b1bb1455fd9dee0744ca81591e988626275652","tid":186261,"uid":115602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"cu natural science 嘅認受性會唔會低過4年制嘅cu science<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n我都想知,想繼續讀postgrad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}